all of this.

167
00:08:57.760 --> 00:09:00.460
OK. so it's a cover-up. Does
it go all the way to the top?

168
00:09:00.560 --> 00:09:03.340
OK. just so you know.
I am aware I am being mocked.

169
00:09:04.480 --> 00:09:05.900
But let me give you
another example

170
00:09:06.000 --> 00:09:09.300
