-Go. Denise!

213
00:13:47.800 --> 00:13:49.780
Oh. some Denise fans in.

214
00:13:49.880 --> 00:13:51.900
Kind of creepy with the shirt.
but still cool.

215
00:13:52.000 --> 00:13:53.580
So I texted my mum to find out

216
00:13:53.680 --> 00:13:55.016
