take this down for the boss.

249
00:15:06.680 --> 00:15:08.780
<i>Four dead. one survivor found.</i>

250
00:15:08.880 --> 00:15:11.020
<i>Kate Reynolds
currently being choppered</i>

251
00:15:11.120 --> 00:15:13.180
